please do it in your dreams.

147
00:07:06,375 --> 00:07:08,917
Don't prejudge and dismiss us.

148
00:07:08,917 --> 00:07:11,208
At least listen to what I have to say.

149
00:07:11,208 --> 00:07:13,375
