about this matter?

150
00:07:14,125 --> 00:07:17,042
DEMON FAMILY, REINCARNATION SEMINAR
Come on, join the demon.

151
00:07:17,042 --> 00:07:19,625
Reincarnation Seminar?

152
00:07:20,167 --> 00:07:22,083
What's with this highly
suspicious seminar?

153
00:07:22,667 --> 00:07:27,625
What are the benefits of no longer being
human and reincarnating as a demon?

154
00:07:27,625 --> 00:07:30,333
Today, I will specially explain it to you.

155
00:07:30,333 --> 00:07:34,000
Let us start with the first perk.

156
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,208
