160
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:46,458
You will be financially secure
if you work for me.

161
00:07:46,458 --> 00:07:49,167
But I still have some savings.

162
00:07:49,167 --> 00:07:51,042
After all, I used to earn a lot.

163
00:07:51,042 --> 00:07:54,042
I won't be out of money for food tomorrow.

164
00:07:54,042 --> 00:07:56,250
Regardless of tomorrow or the day after,

165
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:58,917
what about after ten or twenty years?

166
00:07:58,917 --> 00:08:00,750
It's none of your business.

167
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:03,083
By then, I'll be dead. It doesn't matter.

168
00:08:03,083 --> 00:08:05,583
