which is five times the amount?

181
00:08:37,708 --> 00:08:39,083
Are you serious?

182
00:08:39,083 --> 00:08:40,833
People in the human realm are
going to be so mad.

183
00:08:41,375 --> 00:08:43,083
Hold on, Your Majesty.

184
00:08:43,083 --> 00:08:48,333
No amount of money can buy happiness
without regular work breaks.

185
00:08:48,333 --> 00:08:50,000
You don't have to worry about this.

186
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:54,375
REASONABLE WORK SCHEDULE, NO OVERTIME, FOUR DAYS OFF PER WEEK
All demons are protected and have a comfortable working environment.

187
00:08:54,375 --> 00:08:56,500
A maximum of five hours of work per day.

188
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:58,167
No overtime required.

189
00:08:58,167 --> 00:09:00,208
Four days off every week.

190
00:09:00,208 --> 00:09:01,958
Four days off every week?

191
00:09:01,958 --> 00:09:03,583
It's really great.

192
00:09:03,583 --> 00:09:06,042
You will not only be able to
maintain your private time,

193
00:09:06,042 --> 00:09:09,458
but you will also have so much free time
that you will be at a loss for what to do.

194
00:09:09,458 --> 00:09:12,625
