195
00:09:13,417 --> 00:09:16,500
No, I can't be unfair.

196
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,875
Private and government employees
are treated equally.

197
00:09:19,875 --> 00:09:22,042
This is the right that
demons should enjoy.

198
00:09:22,042 --> 00:09:24,208
Can society function like this?

199
00:09:24,208 --> 00:09:26,542
Of course, it can function, with ease.

200
00:09:26,542 --> 00:09:27,750
Hold on, Your Majesty.

201
00:09:28,375 --> 00:09:30,458
Will work lose its meaning

202
00:09:30,458 --> 00:09:32,958
if the welfare system is
not comprehensive enough?

203
00:09:32,958 --> 00:09:35,792
Of course, our welfare system
is comprehensive.

204
00:09:35,792 --> 00:09:40,292
We guarantee you a house in Jokamachi
or the residential area.

205
00:09:40,292 --> 00:09:44,750
We have clear provisions for license
assistance, maternity, and parental leave.

206
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:48,917
Several other systems are in place
to fully support my subordinates.

207
00:09:48,917 --> 00:09:50,667
So you guys can have children, huh?

208
00:09:50,667 --> 00:09:52,625
What else? Oh ya.

209
00:09:52,625 --> 00:09:54,708
BODY, BRAIN, MAGICAL POWER
A strong body that doesn't get sick,

210
00:09:54,708 --> 00:09:56,625
BODY, BRAIN, MAGICAL POWER
a brain that doesn't age,

211
00:09:56,625 --> 00:09:58,917
BODY, BRAIN, MAGICAL POWER
an endless supply of magical power,

212
00:09:58,917 --> 00:10:03,125
and an immortal soul that can be
resurrected by sleeping.

213
00:10:03,125 --> 00:10:05,875
UNDEAD BODY
Don't skip over the most characteristic part of being a demon.

214
00:10:06,083 --> 00:10:07,708
CONTRACT, AGREE TO BECOME A DEMON
SIGN HERE

215
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:11,625
As long as you become one of us,

216
00:10:11,625 --> 00:10:15,458
you can escape all the troubles
and insecurities of being human,

217
00:10:15,458 --> 00:10:18,000
and the fear of death.

218
00:10:21,125 --> 00:10:22,583
YOU SHOULD JOIN

219
00:10:27,292 --> 00:10:30,958
Come spend eternity with me,

220
00:10:30,958 --> 00:10:32,083
Max.

221
00:10:44,917 --> 00:10:46,125
I'm sorry.

222
00:10:46,125 --> 00:10:47,667
YOU SHOULD JOIN
Let's just forget about this.

223
00:10:49,833 --> 00:10:51,375
Why?

224
00:10:51,375 --> 00:10:53,458
Because you don't want to
be my subordinate?

225
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:57,125
IS IT BAD TO BE A DEMON?
Being a subordinate is just a formality.

226
00:10:57,125 --> 00:10:58,750
IS IT BAD TO BE A DEMON?
We can maintain our current relationship.

227
00:10:59,292 --> 00:11:03,208
Or is it because of what you said
ten years ago about "human dignity"?

228
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:07,667
Is "being human" that important to you?

229
00:11:08,708 --> 00:11:10,417
What is this so-called human dignity?

230
00:11:13,042 --> 00:11:16,125
Don't ask such
a difficult question so bluntly.

231
00:11:16,125 --> 00:11:18,208
Didn't you say this yourself?

232
00:11:18,208 --> 00:11:19,958
I was young and reckless back then.

233
00:11:19,958 --> 00:11:23,125
Even though I spoke with conviction,
I was not sure what I was saying.

234
00:11:23,125 --> 00:11:28,417
I am no longer insisting on being "human."

235
00:11:28,417 --> 00:11:30,083
But how should I say this?

236
00:11:30,083 --> 00:11:33,750
I can't easily give up "myself."

237
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,583
What does that mean?

238
00:11:35,583 --> 00:11:38,250
Even if you reincarnate,
you won't lose your memory.

239
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:42,458
Becoming a demon means
eternal life, wealth, and power.

240
00:11:42,458 --> 00:11:46,750
Then that "me" would no longer be me,
but a different creature.

241
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:49,083
Despite the fact that I was
a very different person

242
00:11:49,083 --> 00:11:51,417
than I was ten years ago.

243
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:57,333
